extendedInfo.description: ** Description **This is beta version of Vee Shopping Plan, that you can use this app to manage you shopping events. You can easily create item list to check or uncheck it.** Feature **- Shopping Plan List- Shopping Item Managements- Check/Uncheck Item- Sort by Important, Alphabhet, etc- Move to Arrange the Item list- Notes, Price and Amount in every Item- Information Result- Share to Other Media- Sent from Email** More Information & Suggestion **Website: www.educastudio.comEmail: andi.taru@gmail.com
